    <item>
      <title>泰晤士水务公司在新的转型计划中面临更严格的监管</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/thames-water-agrees-to-early-special-measures-on-license-breach</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰晤士水务有限公司 (Thames Water Utilities Ltd.) 将很快受到英国监管机构的特别措施，因为这家陷入困境的公司正在竞相寻找新的投资者，以免资金耗尽。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/thames-water-agrees-to-early-special-measures-on-license-breach</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 07:05:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛认为中国供应过剩状况将缓解——但不包括电动汽车</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/goldman-sachs-sees-china-oversupply-easing-just-not-for-evs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛分析师表示，未来几年中国海外商品出口趋势将发生改变，但电动汽车和钢铁行业出口放缓的趋势不太可能得到缓解。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/goldman-sachs-sees-china-oversupply-easing-just-not-for-evs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 06:23:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据消息人士称，菲律宾正与摩根大通就纳入债券指数进行谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/philippines-said-to-be-in-talks-with-jpmorgan-for-bond-index-inclusion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾正在与摩根大通公司进行谈判，希望将其比索政府债券纳入该美国银行的新兴市场债务指标中，该指标由价值数十亿美元的全球基金跟踪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/philippines-said-to-be-in-talks-with-jpmorgan-for-bond-index-inclusion</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 06:00:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行提振市场人气，亚洲股市连续上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/asian-stocks-rise-as-boj-comments-helps-lift-japan-korea-shares</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在日本央行表示如果金融市场不稳定则不会加息之后，亚洲股市在周一全球股市暴跌之后连续第二个交易日上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/asian-stocks-rise-as-boj-comments-helps-lift-japan-korea-shares</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 03:22:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
